title: Oracle Primavera P6 v7
description:
This is Oracle Primavera P7 V7 compatible with Both 64 and 32 bit Windows.
 If you will be choosing the Stand-alone option during the Client Modules installation, you must run setup.exe

No Key or Crack is Required!
During installation you will be asked for a password so enter any password of your choice and it must be more than 8 characters.

 After successful installation restart your Computer and wait until system is fully Loaded and all services are running properly then Run Project Management (Primavera) it will ask you for username/Password so enter (admin) for both username and Password! NOT the password you entered during installation

 If you are facing problem with database connection don't touch anything and restart your computer and run it again if you have the same problem again then you may re-install primavera again!

 And please read comments if you have any problem do not repeat the same question which is already answered!

 Enjoy! and Keep Seeding!
